---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Academics" description="Explore PBASA's student-centered educational program integrating classical academics, arts, and athletics for K-8 students.">

  <PageHero title="Academics" subtitle="A student-centered educational program integrating classical academics, the arts, and athletics." />

  <!-- Intro with Image -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl text-navy-700 leading-relaxed">
            Whether you are looking for support in your child's educational journey, a welcoming community of friends, or a supportive learning environment focused on your child's individual needs, Palm Beach Academy of Sports and Arts offers a unique educational program that integrates strong academics with opportunities in sports and the arts.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
          <img src="/images/classroom.jpeg" alt="Students learning in the classroom" class="w-full h-72 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Educational Program Design -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-navy-50 pt-8">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="gold-divider"></div>
          <span class="text-gold-600 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Program Design</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-navy-900 mb-8">Educational Program Design</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-navy-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            The Palm Beach Academy of Sports and Arts provides a student-centered educational program designed to meet the diverse learning styles, interests, and talents of every student. Our instructional approach emphasizes inquiry-based learning, critical thinking, and problem-solving, encouraging students to ask questions, explore ideas, and take ownership of their learning.
          </p>
          <p>
            The curriculum integrates classical academics, the arts, and athletics across all grade levels. Through interdisciplinary lessons, co-curricular programs, and after-school activities&mdash;including themed clubs and student organizations&mdash;students are given opportunities to develop intellectually, creatively, and physically.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our enriched academic program is designed to provide a well-rounded education that supports students' academic achievement while fostering creativity, collaboration, and personal growth. Palm Beach Academy of Sports and Arts intends to pursue accreditation, ensuring that students in grades K&ndash;8 are well prepared to successfully transition to a variety of high school opportunities upon graduation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Curriculum Areas -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-gold-600 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Curriculum</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-navy-900 mt-3 mb-6">Our Curriculum Includes</h2>
        <div class="gold-divider mx-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Arts -->
        <div class="card p-8 border-t-4 border-gold-500">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gold-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-gold-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">The Arts</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our arts curriculum exposes students to various forms of artistic expression, including visual arts, music, dance, and theater. Through creative exploration, students develop self-expression, aesthetic appreciation, and a deeper understanding of cultural diversity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Sports -->
        <div class="card p-8 border-t-4 border-navy-800">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-navy-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Sports</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">
            Physical education and sports programs promote physical fitness, teamwork, discipline, and sportsmanship. We offer a range of sports opportunities that cater to diverse interests, ensuring that every student can find their passion and develop essential life skills.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Classical Education -->
        <div class="card p-8 border-t-4 border-gold-500">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gold-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-gold-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5h12M9 3v2m1.048 9.5A18.022 18.022 0 016.412 9m6.088 9h7M11 21l5-10 5 10M12.751 5C11.783 10.77 8.07 15.61 3 18.129" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Classical Education (Spanish)</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">
            Students will explore Spanish culture, acquire proficiency in understanding and communicating in the language, and potentially apply this skill in their career or as an additional life skill, contributing to their personal success journey.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Themed Months -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-navy-900 text-white">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="text-gold-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Innovation</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-heading font-bold mt-3 mb-6">Themed Topic Months</h2>
          <div class="gold-divider mx-auto mb-6"></div>
          <p class="text-navy-200 text-lg">
            To create innovative opportunities for all students, uniquely themed school-wide topic months serve as the basis of specialized sports, arts, and classical education activities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-navy-800/50 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-navy-700/50">
            <div class="text-gold-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">September</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold mb-2">Classical Education Month</h3>
            <p class="text-navy-300 text-sm">National Hispanic Heritage Month</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-800/50 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-navy-700/50">
            <div class="text-gold-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">October</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold mb-2">Arts Month</h3>
            <p class="text-navy-300 text-sm">National Arts &amp; Humanities Month</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-800/50 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-navy-700/50">
            <div class="text-gold-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">May</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold mb-2">Sports Month</h3>
            <p class="text-navy-300 text-sm">National Fitness and Sports Month</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gold-50 text-center">
    <div class="container-narrow max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-navy-900 mb-6">Ready to Give Your Child a Well-Rounded Education?</h2>
      <p class="text-navy-600 text-lg mb-8">Pre-enrollment is open. Discover the PBASA difference today.</p>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1CuhqVLxdc6ujO8y3FLcWLoVdVuoKK6SDI2h0ay5Hulo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-navy text-lg">
        Pre-Enroll Now
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
